      **************************************                            00077600
       2000-PROCESO.                                                    00077700

            PERFORM 2500-I-APAREO THRU 2500-F-APAREO.

            IF WS-CLI-CLAVE = HIGH-VALUE AND WS-NOV-CLAVE = HIGH-VALUE
               SET WS-FIN-LECTURA TO TRUE
            END-IF.

       F-2000-PROCESO. EXIT.
      **************************************
