      **************************************
       2500-I-APAREO.

           IF WS-SI

             IF WS-CLI-CLAVE = WS-NOV-CLAVE                              0007800
               ADD WS-CLI-SALDO TO CLI-SALDO GIVING WS-SUMA-SALDO
               PERFORM 4000-I-LEER-NOV THRU 4000-F-LEER-NOV              0007850

             ELSE                                                        0007870

               IF WS-CLI-CLAVE > WS-NOV-CLAVE                            0007910
                 PERFORM 4000-I-LEER-NOV THRU 4000-F-LEER-NOV            0007850

               ELSE                                                      0007960
                 ADD 1 TO WS-NOVEDADES-NOTFOUND
                 DISPLAY 'NOVEDAD NO ENCONTRADA PARA CLIENTE ACTUAL.'
                 MOVE REG-CLIENTE-VSAM-IN TO REG-CLIENTES
                 PERFORM 5000-I-GRABAR-SALIDA THRU 5000-F-GRABAR-SALIDA  0007980
                 INITIALIZE WS-SUMA-SALDO
                 PERFORM 3000-I-LEER-CLI THRU 3000-F-LEER-CLI            0008010

